                  </hi>. I live at 7, Amos Terrace, Leytonstone, which is next door but one to No. 9.—I have known Murray for twelve months at No. 9—he lived there in the name of Munroe for about twelve months before he was taken in charge—and was living there with his wife and family when he was arrested.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18770409-name-368" type="witnessName">
